  <AbilityBonus InternalName="EF_ShardAffinity">
    <AbilityBonusType>Unit_Design</AbilityBonusType>
    <AbilityBonusOption InternalName="EF_ShardAffinity">
      <Type>Faction Trait</Type>
      <IsCombatAbility>1</IsCombatAbility>
      <DisplayName>Shard Affinity</DisplayName>
      <Description>When defending any city with an elemental shard shrine (or any improvement that produces shard power) inside the city walls, melee attacks from this unit deals 2 additional magic damage (fire=fire, water=cold, air=lightning, earth=poison). Multiple types stack, but more than one of each type does nothing. Life shards do not add any damage. The extra damage does not appear in Unit Details, but it is added when striking enemies in battle. 

This trait cannot be selected at the same time as Lust for Power.</Description>
      <Icon>Ability_Attunement_Icon.png</Icon>
      <GameModifier>
        <ModType>Unit</ModType>
        <Attribute>AdjustUnitStat</Attribute>
        <StrVal>UnitStat_Attack_Cold</StrVal>
        <StrVal2>ExpandedTraits_FLAG_DefendingACityWithWaterShard</StrVal2>
        <Value>2</Value>
        <vsLower>1</vsLower>
        <Provides>When defending any city with an elemental shard shrine (or any improvement that produces shard power) inside the city walls, melee attacks from this unit deals 2 additional magic damage (fire=fire, water=cold, air=lightning, earth=poison). Multiple types stack, but more than one of each type does nothing. Life shards do not add any damage. The extra damage does not appear in Unit Details, but it is added when striking enemies in battle. 

This trait cannot be selected at the same time as Lust for Power.</Provides>
      </GameModifier>
      <GameModifier>
        <ModType>Unit</ModType>
        <Attribute>AdjustUnitStat</Attribute>
        <StrVal>UnitStat_Attack_Poison</StrVal>
        <StrVal2>ExpandedTraits_FLAG_DefendingACityWithEarthShard</StrVal2>
        <Value>2</Value>
        <vsLower>1</vsLower>
        <Provides>.</Provides>
      </GameModifier>
      <GameModifier>
        <ModType>Unit</ModType>
        <Attribute>AdjustUnitStat</Attribute>
        <StrVal>UnitStat_Attack_Fire</StrVal>
        <StrVal2>ExpandedTraits_FLAG_DefendingACityWithFireShard</StrVal2>
        <Value>2</Value>
        <vsLower>1</vsLower>
        <Provides>.</Provides>
      </GameModifier>
      <GameModifier>
        <ModType>Unit</ModType>
        <Attribute>AdjustUnitStat</Attribute>
        <StrVal>UnitStat_Attack_Lightning</StrVal>
        <StrVal2>ExpandedTraits_FLAG_DefendingACityWithAirShard</StrVal2>
        <Value>2</Value>
        <vsLower>1</vsLower>
        <Provides>.</Provides>
      </GameModifier>
      <AdditionalTrainingTurns>10</AdditionalTrainingTurns>
      <Prereq>
        <Type>Race</Type>
        <Attribute>Race_Type_Angel</Attribute>
      </Prereq>
      <AIData AIPersonality="AI_General">
        <AIPriority>6</AIPriority>
      </AIData>
    </AbilityBonusOption>
    <AbilityBonusOption InternalName="EF_LustForPower">
      <Type>Faction Trait</Type>
      <DisplayName>Lust for Power</DisplayName>
      <Description>When attacking a city with a shard shrine (or any improvement that produces shard power) inside the city walls, this unit gains +20 Accuracy against all defenders. 

This trait cannot be selected at the same time as Shard Affinity.</Description>
      <Icon>Ability_Attunement_Icon.png</Icon>
      <GameModifier>
        <ModType>Unit</ModType>
        <Attribute>AdjustUnitStat</Attribute>
        <StrVal>UnitStat_Accuracy</StrVal>
        <StrVal2>ExpandedTraits_FLAG_DefendingACityWithAnyShard</StrVal2>
        <Value>20</Value>
        <vsHigher>1</vsHigher>
        <Provides>When attacking a city with a shard shrine (or any improvement that produces shard power) inside the city walls, this unit gains +20 Accuracy against all defenders. 

This trait cannot be selected at the same time as Shard Affinity.</Provides>
      </GameModifier>
      <AdditionalTrainingTurns>10</AdditionalTrainingTurns>
      <Prereq>
        <Type>Race</Type>
        <Attribute>Race_Type_Angel</Attribute>
      </Prereq>
      <AIData AIPersonality="AI_General">
        <AIPriority>4</AIPriority>
      </AIData>
    </AbilityBonusOption>
  </AbilityBonus>
  <AbilityBonus InternalName="EF_OneTrueGod">
    <AbilityBonusType>Unit_Design</AbilityBonusType>
    <AbilityBonusOption InternalName="EF_OneTrueGod">
      <Type>Faction Trait</Type>
      <DisplayName>Holy War</DisplayName>
      <IsCombatAbility>1</IsCombatAbility>
      <Description>This unit gains +25 Accuracy and Spell mastery when trying to attack or cast spells against any God that is not the One True God. In addition, this unit gains +20 accuracy against any Summoned units. If the target is both Summoned and a God, the bonus to Accuracy stacks for a total +45 (spell mastery bonus only against Gods). </Description>
      <GameModifier>
        <ModType>Unit</ModType>
        <Attribute>AdjustUnitStat</Attribute>
        <StrVal>UnitStat_Accuracy</StrVal>
        <StrVal2>UnitStat_BG_IsGod</StrVal2>
        <Value>25</Value>
        <vsHigher>1</vsHigher>
        <Provides>This unit gains +25 Accuracy and Spell mastery when trying to attack or cast spells against any God that is not the One True God. In addition, this unit gains +20 accuracy against any Summoned units. If the target is both Summoned and a God, the bonus to Accuracy stacks for a total +45 (spell mastery bonus only against Gods)</Provides>
      </GameModifier>
      <GameModifier>
        <ModType>Unit</ModType>
        <Attribute>AdjustUnitStat</Attribute>
        <StrVal>UnitStat_MagicPower</StrVal>
        <StrVal2>UnitStat_BG_IsGod</StrVal2>
        <Provides>.</Provides>
        <Value>25</Value>
        <vsHigher>1</vsHigher>
      </GameModifier>
      <GameModifier>
        <ModType>Unit</ModType>
        <Attribute>AdjustUnitStat</Attribute>
        <StrVal>UnitStat_Accuracy</StrVal>
        <StrVal2>UnitStat_BG_IsSummoned</StrVal2>
        <Provides>.</Provides>
        <Value>20</Value>
        <vsHigher>1</vsHigher>
      </GameModifier>
      <AdditionalTrainingTurns>10</AdditionalTrainingTurns>
      <Icon>Ability_DeathWorship_Icon.png</Icon>
      <HideWhenUpgraded>1</HideWhenUpgraded>
      <Prereq>
        <Type>Race</Type>
        <Attribute>Race_Type_Angel</Attribute>
      </Prereq>
      <AIData AIPersonality="AI_General">
        <AIPriority>1</AIPriority>
      </AIData>
    </AbilityBonusOption>
  </AbilityBonus>
